rect.aria-label: Earnings of Supermart Grocery Stores, , Scatter plot with 519 points. Use the arrow keys to navigate chart information and Tab to access the chart content.
X axisshows Sales and ranges from 500 to 2750.
Y axisshows Profit and ranges from 0 to 1250.
Legendshows Food Category and has values Bakery, Beverages, Eggs, Meat & Fish, Food Grains, Fruits & Veggies, Oil & Masala, and Snacks.
